headline.print_headline: Gray Sets Down First 11; Padres Beat A's 6-5
headline.main: Gray Sets Down First 11; Padres Beat A's 6-5

lead_paragraph: Sonny Gray retired the first 11 in four scoreless innings and Jed Lowrie hit his first home run of the spring for Oakland on Tuesday before the San Diego Padres rallied for a 6-5 victory over the Athletics.
